data.description:
Welcome to your dream home on a little over 2 acres of scenic countryside, where rustic charm meets modern elegance. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts polished concrete floors and countertops throughout, blending contemporary style with natural beauty. Step inside to an open living area, offering ample space for your KING SIZE furniture and easy maintenance with sleek concrete floors. 
Outside, enjoy entertaining in your private oasis with an above-ground pool and a charming pergola for relaxation. The property also features a spacious 40 x 60 shop, perfect for storage or creative pursuits. A new retaining wall enhances curb appeal and ensures the property's longevity.
Experience the essence of country living, just minutes away from Skiatook Lake. This meticulously crafted home offers a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and outdoor enjoyment you don't want to miss! Your ideal home​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ awaits!
